  "special": {
    "title": "Putting trouble on the run.",
    "description": "Always shock. Fires multiple orbs that rapidly converge into a short tornado. Each pellet explodes on impact, dealing splash equal to 40% of weapon damage. That splash is treated as grenade damage and scales with grenade-damage bonuses."
  },
  "notes": "Its spiral path can let Zer0 score multiple hits with B0re. Each pellet creates its own splash hit worth 40% of weapon damage. This splash counts as grenade damage, can trigger Blood Bath, and benefits from grenade-damage bonuses. It is also very strong on Gaige, since the pattern can trigger The Nth Degree repeatedly and then chain through Close Enough. Aiming at the ground or a second target can increase those procs.",
